	<tr><td class=bodycopy>

The same rules as for <a href=<PAGE>about_empire>Empire</a> apply, except as noted below.
<ol>
<li> Cuba starts with a fleet in each of its home centers, including Holguin.
<li> Quebec starts with an army in Ungava instead of a fleet.
</ol>
		<!--BODYCOPY ENDS HERE-->
